# Fetched diffs and labelled JSONs are populated per-run by
# scripts/collect_oss_diffs.mjs and labelled by the operator. They are NOT
# checked in — the upstream license terms vary by repo and we don't want to
# accidentally redistribute a copyleft diff in MIT-licensed security-audit.
#
# Keep this file and README.md tracked; ignore everything else.
diffs/
expected/
!.gitignore
!README.md
